			<p>The app contains all the information you need to know about the hilda Neo card. A tutorial guides you smoothly through running the test, you will find information about how the card works and why your using it, what LDH is and why it is a critical indicator of the health of a new born baby.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="column col6 edge" style='margin-top: 10px'>
			<p>After testing the results are stored and accessible at any time. You are able to email results within a trusted network. The color of the result indicates if the result is within range or not. The result expands to see more information about LDH or Bilirubin.</p>
